'''Thorn fever''' was a deadly virus with no known cure. When thorn fever spread on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tallek]], the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] rounded up anyone who caught the disease and let them [[Death/Legends|die]] in isolation camps.

